content: Hey everyone, with last days of EPF cohort three, I just want to remind you about the last Office Hours tomorrow. Check the agenda in the issue, it will be an opportunity for you to share closing updates and summaries of your projects. And also, please don't forget to submit your Final Dev Update if you haven't done so yet, details in the pinned message https://discord.com/channels/595666850260713488/843176491386667018/1075832242909225001
